{"tid":895626,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【學生動源召集人遇襲事件】","createTime":"2018-11-09T10:45:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-09T13:18:05.000Z","uid":153615,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a9caaaa9dd8f3d9646b6faee9768dd304d9784fc","tid":895626,"uid":153615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T10:45:40.000Z","msg":"【學生動源召集人遇襲事件】<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/09/184516_54bc49e253dd7f8c91b316eb1d376b00.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F09%2F184516_54bc49e253dd7f8c91b316eb1d376b00.jpg&h=a40ce1e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日約上午七點三十五分時，敝組織召集人於元朗住所返回學校時，於離住所不足三十秒路程的地點遭一名全黑衣著戴口罩圓框眼鏡男子快步走近並撞撃肩膀，其後再推撞並揮動拳頭施襲，其間左手及面部受襲並令眼鏡飛脫。<br />\n<br />\n施襲後該名男子企圖離開，敝組織召集人試圖追截並拍低其面容時該名男子試圖從召集人手中奪去電話阻止拍攝，並企圖再次施襲，隨後敝組織召集人致電報案中心時該名男子疑似得知並快跑逃逸。<br />\n<br />\n及後警方到場後陪同敝組織召集人到博愛醫院驗傷以及返回元朗警署錄取口供。<br />\n<br />\n於是次事件發生前，近一個星期均有多名不明男子在下午放學時分於施襲地點守候，事件發生後敝組織相信這些男子與本次事件有關，企圖得知敝組織召集人出入時間方便施襲。<br />\n<br />\n學生動源在此呼籲有關人士停止暴力行為，我等並不會因此而放棄獨立之路，我們不會畏懼暴力，愈要我收聲我就愈大聲，光明必然會戰勝黑暗，正義將會重臨香港。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/studentlocalism/posts/2269725709769167\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstudentlocalism%2Fposts%2F2269725709769167&d=AikRqUF0ABqfijWhCN2gDZUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=21a6fcb4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/studentlocalism/posts/2269725709769167</a>"},{"pid":"d60abbe08c65c8142850898e444f1d03d53566c1","tid":895626,"uid":78533,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T10:59:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8ddf61ba2c89fe2cf56c8297c7adc63126428c4","tid":895626,"uid":40628,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T11:43:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1facc310b57d64f31faa3d10cf0dadaeaf6a6ba6","tid":895626,"uid":40628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d8ddf61ba2c89fe2cf56c8297c7adc63126428c4","tid":895626,"uid":40628,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T11:43:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T11:44:38.000Z","msg":"一齊反抗吧"},{"pid":"4181f44929ea3a4dd1102ad67c365e320a4be9bf","tid":895626,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T12:49:13.000Z","msg":"加油！"},{"pid":"21db6385a9438d44317913a2caf1ba830d34cd47","tid":895626,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T12:51:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d3e149a9cfef99021c56287ea5bd7ef0e7eeb293","tid":895626,"uid":34410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T13:17:43.000Z","msg":"共狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa67103b7e8e1126b9f931eeec183859939b5252","tid":895626,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T13:18:05.000Z","msg":"或可考慮習武強身<br />\n泰拳基本上係最快見效及最實際既武術<br />\n<br />\n帶武器反而有被黑警屈既風險"}]}